description: Introducing the 16 FORD MUSTANG GT Hot Wheels edition! Get ready to rev up your collection with this sleek and powerful die-cast car. Inspired by the iconic Ford Mustang GT, this Hot Wheels model features incredible detail and craftsmanship. Its striking design, complete with signature Mustang styling cues, captures the essence of speed and performance.

sellerEmail: Experience the thrill of the TOYOTA AE86 Sprinter Trueno! This Hot Wheels die-cast car pays homage to the iconic AE86, known for its agile handling and striking design. With its pop-up headlights and signature panda-style livery, this model captures the essence of Japanese racing heritage. A must-have for car enthusiasts and collectors, the AE86 Sprinter Trueno embodies timeless automotive excellence. Ignite your passion for cars with this remarkable piece.

toyName: Hot Wheels Action Figure-8 Track Set
description: Measuring in at more than two-feet tall, the Hot Wheels® Vertical-8 Jump track set features two different paths to stunt and race. Kids flip a manual diverter to choose between a vertical U-turn with two stunt jumps or a figure-8 path before landing in a catch cup with a big finish. It includes 1 Hot Wheels® vehicle and connects to other sets. Additional sets sold separately, subject to availability. Colors and decorations may vary.

toyName: Hot Wheels Track Set, City Ultimate Garage Playset, Parking For 100+ Cars
description: The Hot Wheels™ City Ultimate Garage is 3 feet tall, offering endless storytelling and vehicle action play! The enormous toy garage has parking for up to 100+ vehicles and a Robo T-Rex nemesis that fuels kids' imagination.

sellerEmail: Unleash the power and precision of the McLaren Senna! This Hot Wheels die-cast car captures the essence of the legendary supercar. With its aerodynamic design, sleek lines, and iconic Papaya Orange color, the McLaren Senna is a true symbol of automotive engineering excellence.

description: Get ready to ignite your passion for speed and style with the McLaren 720S! This Hot Wheels die-cast car captures the essence of the iconic supercar in stunning detail.
